column6: FINAL ISSUE!  WHO IS DOCTOR OCTOPUS?! As the good Doctor resurfaces in Spidey's life in ORIGIN OF THE SPECIES, get a glimpse into how Doc Ock came to be the multi-armed maniacal menace he is! THEN -- CAN MARY JANE RESCUE SPIDER-MAN?!  When Doc Tramma, Mr. Negative's scientist supreme and femme fatale, targeted the life of Mary Jane Watson, she kidnapped her ex-beau, Peter Parker!  With the help of THE BLACK CAT, MJ's prepared to rescue the Amazing Spider-Man! Rated T  ...$3.99
